author: Frederik I, King of Denmark and Norway, 1471-1533
title: En Vidisse aff Kong Fredericks fulde Mactzbreff, so[m] han gaff Her Knud Gyldensterne Electo till Othens Stict, Her Mogens Gyldenstierne, Her Niels Löcke Riddere, Regnolt fan Hederstorff öffverste och Principale Hoffuitzmend for hans krigis folk til Norge
